text.tspan: Number of fatalities from terrorism-related attacks
Total number of fatalities per year from terrorist attacks. This represents the number of total confirmed fatalities for
the incident. This includes all victims and attackers who died as a direct result of the incident.
Source: Terrorism Fatalities- Global Terrorism Database
